## *A checklist that could be useful*

- [ ]  Create a Lambda function that listens for the creation of a .csv file in an S3 bucket and uploads the content of the file into an RDS Mysql database.
- [ ]  Ensure the database credentials are not hard-coded into the Lambda function.
- [ ]  Make sure the database is publicly accessible.
- [ ]  Download, zip and copy the pymysql code to S3.
- [ ]  Write Lambda function code using environment variables (OPTION A).
- [ ]  Write Lambda function code using Secrets Manager (OPTION B).
- [ ]  Create a MySQL table for the exercise.
- [ ]  Set up role permission policies for the project.
